room_title: Escape room "The Lost Jewel of Zanzibar" by Countdown 2 Escape in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: It is 1930. Your colleague, Magnus Ferguson has been exploring throughout Africa searching for antiquities. He has made a wondrous discovery but it is in danger of falling into the hands of a ruthless and dishonest warlord. Magnus has hidden the jewel in his camp and left clues that only YOU will be able to interpret.
